# 4. Engineering Philosophy

AFAT-X10 is built around four principles:

### 1. Flow Capture

Use incoming airflow as an energy source.

### 2. Pressure Concentration

Increase usable pressure through controlled geometry.

### 3. Velocity Amplification

Accelerate flow through narrowing channels.

### 4. Structural Stabilization

Use airflow management to improve aircraft balance.

